1. Ne mogu više da se borim, *odustajem*! (I can't fight anymore, *I'm giving up*!)
2. *Odustajem* od ove ideje, nije realna. (*I'm abandoning* this idea, it's not realistic.)
3. Nemoj odustajati, upornost se isplati! (Don't give up, persistence pays off!)
4. Oni su *odustali* od planova za letovanje. (They *abandoned* their plans for a summer vacation.)
5. *Odustajem* od dalje diskusije, ovo nije konstruktivno. (*I'm giving up* on further discussion, this isn't constructive.)
6. Iako su bile umorne, nisu *odustajale* od cilja. (Although they were tired, they didn't *give up* on their goal.)
7. Ako *odustaneš* sada, propustićeš veliku priliku. (If you *give up* now, you'll miss a great opportunity.)
8. Nažalost, moram *odustati* od dolaska na proslavu. (Unfortunately, I have to *give up* on coming to the celebration.)